{"tid":1518753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"筆架山現「平反暴動」直幡","createTime":"2019-08-30T10:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:41:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a91c3e2cba417b5538f1ba3753f7a27c86b6dc8","tid":1518753,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:40:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190830/20758715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F20758715&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=1a1aa47f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F20758715&h=6e830897\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190830/20758715</a><br />\n<br />\n筆架山現「平反暴動」直幡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190830/large/1567095328_2907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190830%2Flarge%2F1567095328_2907.jpg&h=44fe6090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】無懼暴政香港人走上街頭抗爭，發生多次警民衝突事件，昨早上6時許，有心人於筆架山龍翔道近豐力樓的懸崖上，出現兩幅約八米乘兩米的直幡，黃底黑字寫上「平反暴動釋放義士」。<br />\n<br />\n至上午9時許，消防派員到場拆除該直幡，約半小時後完成拆除。警方表示，案件列作發現橫額，交由相關部門跟進。<br />\n翁鈺輝攝 <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鍾稱不信任警方 擬自行追查<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n政府遏自決 學者料DQ不手軟<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n遊行發起人憶扣恐怖囚室<br />\n<br />\n鍾稱不信任警方 擬自行追查<br />\n逼和理非變勇武 為緊急法鋪路<br />\n爆眼少女：冀港人遠離痛苦<br />\n傘運對話中伏 岑敖暉：勿信林鄭<br />\nIT界：《緊急法》封網摧毀互聯網產業<br />\n郭榮鏗警告：勢令外商撤資<br />\n至少90中學響應9.3罷課<br />\n和理非喇沙仔「公義比學業重要」<br />\n15歲衝衝子 留守護「童子軍」<br />\n40教堂9.1鳴鐘盼喚醒林鄭良知<br />\n國泰鼓吹篤灰 罷工即炒<br />\n美孚連儂牆衝突 三人被捕<br />\n將軍澳舞刀漢威嚇黃絲街坊<br />\n蘋論：極限施壓 中共畫虎不成反類犬<br />\n陳浩天被指傷人 機場離境遭拘捕<br />\n放映會後警署外聚集 深水埗10人被捕<br />\n女碩士生路過被捕 遭脫內褲搜身「要見私處才放過我」<br />\n難到內地實習 中醫夢恐碎<br />\n戰術背心遮編號 警︰郁得多移位<br />\n擎槍光頭警赴京 十．一做上賓<br />\n解放軍換防 海陸空進駐本港<br />\n撐反送中台灣人 疑深圳失蹤<br />\n戴耀廷籲和勇協作「打好世界波」<br />\n素人積極戰區選 風雲計劃停運<br />\n政府遏自決 學者料DQ不手軟<br />\n遊行發起人憶扣恐怖囚室<br />\n地政署促白衣村民還官地<br />\n向美領館潑墨 雙程漢囚兩周<br />\n8.31遊行受打壓 民陣岑子杰遭伏擊一日兩宗 鍾健平踢保後被打"},{"pid":"766898ecf5a6387ba0ba557eca860ef88ce8a009","tid":1518753,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=1881475a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=718112f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=8681ff33\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d90a6ce6c6c36d23e1a092d30e6786b741e2073e","tid":1518753,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size